div.h2: Double Fault & Exception Chaining: Triple Fault Anatomy

g.text: IDT Gate States That Cause Double Fault

div.p: COLLISION: Timer tick (55ms after STI) invokes CPU Vector 8 = Double Fault Handler immediately triggers TRIPLE FAULT REBOOT
v=20 e=0000 i=1 IRQ0 timer at vector 32 v=21 e=0000 i=1 IRQ1 keyboard at vector 33
v=08 e=0000 Double Fault at vector 8! v=08 e=0000 Double Fault again! [QEMU reboot] Triple fault reset
v=0d e=0000 GPF from bad IDT entry v=08 e=0000 Double Fault [QEMU reboot] Triple fault
